# Route Structure Rule

When editing the application:

- Keep routes/pages under the frontend route structure defined in `architecture.md`.
- Keep API routes under backend router structure defined in `architecture.md`.
- Do not introduce ad-hoc route folders outside approved module boundaries.
- If generated files land in wrong module, move them to the approved location and fix imports.
